        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 14. Levinsenia tribranchiata (ESFM-POL/2013-1171). A, B, Antero-lateral view of branchial chaetigers; C, No- topodium of first chaetiger with lateral sense organ and notopodial postchaetal lobe; D, First branchial chaetiger with lateral sense organ and notopodial postchaetal lobe emerging on branchia; E, Parapodium from a posterior chaetiger with modified neurochaetae, lateral sense organ and notopodial postchaetal lobe. Scale bar: A, 71 µm; B, 38 µm; C, 13 µm; D, 14 µm; E, 10 µm. Abbreviations: ant, anterior; bran, branchiae; lso, lateral sense organ; ntpcl, notopodial postchaetal lobe; mneuc, modified neurochaetae; post, posterior." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4438167/files/figure.png" .

